The paper discusses the challenges of handling large and complex scientific data sets in a research institution and the development of a Laboratory Information Management System (LIMS) to address those challenges. This topic is relevant to several sub-categories of computer science, including database systems (cs.DB), information retrieval (cs.IR), distributed and parallel computing (cs.DC), software engineering (cs.SE), and computer engineering (cs.CE).
